{"title":"Ubuntu截图工具","num_read":163,"num_like":657,"num_collection":788,"num_comments":94,"slug":"resource-system-Linux-UbuntuFlameshot","date":"2019-09-27T16:00:00.000Z","img":"/img/header_img/15.gif","_id":"clhrbp2g900k3o5lggrkiamed","project":"Linux","site":{"data":{}},"updated":"2022-09-20T02:26:21.650Z","author":"Sunfy","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/resource-system-Linux-UbuntuFlameshot.json","webPath":"2019/09/28/resource-system-Linux-UbuntuFlameshot/","permalink":"https://sunfy9.gitee.io/2019/09/28/resource-system-Linux-UbuntuFlameshot/","excerpt":"Linux系统Ubuntu截图工具推荐使用 ","covers":["../../../../img/UbuntuFlameshot/image-20201020151914799.png","../../../../img/UbuntuFlameshot/image-20201020152205127.png","../../../../img/UbuntuFlameshot/image-20201020152406303.png","../../../../img/UbuntuFlameshot/image-20201020152618648.png"],"keywords":"sunfy, hexo-theme-snail","content":"<p>Linux系统Ubuntu截图工具推荐使用 </p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h3><p>Windows上习惯了QQ的截图工具，本工具类似QQ截图工具功能，在习惯QQ截图的情况下可以很方便的使用。效果图：<img src=\"../../../../img/UbuntuFlameshot/image-20201020151914799.png\" alt=\"image-20201020151914799\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装过程\"><a href=\"#安装过程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装过程\"></a>安装过程</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install flameshot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"启动命令\"><a href=\"#启动命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动命令\"></a>启动命令<sunfy-line></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">flameshot gui</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"设置快捷方式\"><a href=\"#设置快捷方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置快捷方式\"></a>设置快捷方式</h3><p><img src=\"../../../../img/UbuntuFlameshot/image-20201020152205127.png\" a